  "description": "<h3>Nintendo.com Description (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/monster-band/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3><br><br><p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\n      Do you want to travel the world? Do you want millions of people to know \n      your name and to sing your songs? Do you want to become a pop star? Make \n      your dreams come true!\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\n      You are the leader of the hottest new band around. But, before you can \n      make the charts you have to get creative. Compose your own music on 3 \n      different instruments, learn to play famous songs and have tons of fun \n      playing together with your friends. Make your wish come true – the stage \n      is yours!\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      <b>Features</b>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"padding-left: 25.0px; margin-top: 0\">\n      • Learn and play famous songs and styles• Play 3 different \n      instruments and write your own songs (single or multi-player function)• \n      Play solo mode, or join your friends for co-op or duel play\n    </p>",
